doctype html
html
  head
    title
      | Charcuterie
    script(type="text/javascript" src=".././script.js")
    link(rel='stylesheet' href='.././styles/stylesheet.min.css')
    //FONTS
    link(href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato&subset=latin,latin-ext' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css')
    link(rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com")
    link(href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet")
  body
    div.wrapper
      div.container
        // HEADER NAV START
        header.main-header
          nav.navbar
            div.hidden-logo
              h1 CHARCUTERIE
              a.icon(href="javascript:void(0);" onClick="myFunction()")
                | &#9776;
            div.nav-container
              div.buttons
                -const siteLinks = ["WELCOME", "MENU", "REVIEWS"]
                for link, i in siteLinks
                  a.navButton(href="#")= link
              div.logo-nav
                h1 CHARCUTERIE
              div.buttons
                -const contactLinks = ["RESERVATIONS", "ORDER NOW"]
                for link, i in contactLinks
                  a.navButton(href="#")= link
        // END HEADER NAV
        // FULL WIDTH HERO IMAGE
        div.main-content-wrapper
          div.hero-image-container
            //-This is just a placeholder for now
            img.hero-image(src='../fork-spoon-food.jpg', width='100%')
            
        // END HERO IMAGE
        // ABOUT SECTION
        div.about-wrapper
          div.about-content-container
            | When in need for a comforting night in, be sure to pick up a homecooked meal from Charcuterie. Chef Charlotte Castillo invites you to experience true, authentic filipino cuisine, cooked straight from her home kitchen. Using only the freshest ingredients provided by Mountain House soil, Charcuterie is a must try if you are in the area.
          
        
        
